  "body": "It’s not like the others as in, it’s not a real package. Doesn’t have `package.json` in the root.\r\nI figured we might as well flatten it. This will make importing less annoying if we drop Haste.\r\n\r\nOld structure:\r\n\r\n```\r\npackages\r\n- shared\r\n  - src\r\n    - event\r\n      ...\r\n    - utils\r\n      ...\r\n    ...\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\nNew structure:\r\n\r\n```\r\npackages\r\n- shared\r\n  - event\r\n    ...\r\n  ...\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe `utils` folder was unnecessary and we used it inconsistently. I didn’t see much use in it so I flattened it into the root folder.",
